---
title: Sugar Shack Maple and Cheese Curd Beyond Meat® Burgers with Maple-Mustard Roasted Potatoes
description: All aboard the sugar shack express! This meal inspired by the Quebecois feast celebrates the magic of maple syrup. We've also borrowed flavours from another Quebecois fave—poutine. The Beyond Meat® patty is seared and then cooked in a rich gravy while squeaky cheese curds melt on top. A side of roasted potatoes tossed in a maple-mustard butter completes this feast.
